Title: Portugal. Lost In Time
DateModified: '2019-03-09'
DatePublished: '2019-03-09'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/portugal-lost-in-time
SetInCountry: Portugal
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Darrelynn Klashinsky
AuthorCountry: Canada
Text: "A venture unravelling secrets from the past.  Excursions to the medieval fortresses\
  \ to bohemian architecture to uncover designs of beauty and grandeur.  To follow\
  \ the path of scenic beauty of pristine beaches and rugged landscape.  Intertwined\
  \ with amazing culture and lifestyle of the people who grace this country.  To uncover\
  \ forgotten dreams of a land lost in translation.  \nExploring the amazing diversity\
  \ from pristine beaches of Algarve and caves, strolling cobbled alleyways of Porto\
  \ and inspired by a fairytale ambience Sinatra.  Into the remote Estremadura and\
  \ olive groves of Alentejo.  \nInspired by Lisbon\u2019s the Baixa, the traditional\
  \ center of city life.  Hidden in this corner of the world exist Lisbon\u2019s oldest\
  \ shops.  With tradesmen and craftsmen in business for centuries.  The charm and\
  \ nostalgia if each quaint village will open the door to dreams yet to be uncovered.\
  \  In this far away place of dreams and history.  \nWith the new renaissance hip\
  \ new restaurants and glorious hotels also introduce a modern edge if that is your\
  \ preference.  Explore the fun and exciting newness of every new experience.  Venturing\
  \ back in time to discover all that was forgotten."
